To embed dashboards on the Lightning Home tab and in Lightning apps:

* Customize Application
	+ Add a Sales Pipeline dashboard to the Home tab for sales teams
	+ Embedded dashboards are fully interactive
	+ Dashboards need space to display charts and tables
* From Setup, enter App Builder and select Lightning App Builder
* Choose where to embed the dashboard (app page or home tab)
* Give your app page or home tab layout a label
* Drag and drop the Dashboard component into place
* Select a dashboard to embed
* Optionally specify a maximum height and show/hide error loading
* Click Save, Activate

Change Dashboard Owner
